item.title: About
item.description: Who am I? Hello, I’m Jonathan Wash. I’m a support engineer for a construction company by day and a technology enthusiast by night. I’ll be experimenting my experiences on this blog and trying to document everything I do so that other people can hopefully find some help with things… if not only for me to remind me how and why the hell I did things. The Tech Behind the Blog This blog is running on GitHub Pages using Hugo as the static generator:
